cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.CL

This paper is primarily focused on Federated Learning (FL), which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses strategies for reducing communication costs, which could fall under Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of FL in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), which could also be relevant categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of compression techniques for communication, which could fall under Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) if the compression is applied to text data.
